data.description: Price reduction!  Where comfort meets sophistication! This 5bedroom, 4.5-bath residence spans 4,100 sq ft, offering a perfect blend of space and style.  The heart of this home is the gourmet kitchen–a warm and inviting space designed for both casual meals and grand entertaining. Top-of-the-line appliances and stylish finishes make this kitchen a chef's dream.  The bedrooms are generously sized, providing cozy retreats for restful nights. The primary suite is a haven of relaxation, featuring a spacious layout and a luxurious private bath. The remaining baths showcase modern design and functionality, perfect for the demands of daily life.  The finished lower level adds versatility to the property - large multi-purpose room currently being used as a gym with rubber floor.  A bedroom, walk-in closet, full bath and unfinished storage complete the level.  Lots of space for entertaining with a large patio and deck.  Solar panels make it economical!
